{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:25:26.884552+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here is every CIFAR-10 model implemented in the `models/` directory of this repository, together with its reported accuracy from the README:\n\n| # | Model | Accuracy |\n|---|-------|----------|\n| 1 | [VGG16](https://arxiv.org/abs/1409.1556) | 92.64% |\n| 2 | [ResNet18](https://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385) | 93.02% |\n| 3 | [ResNet50](https://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385) | 93.62% |\n| 4 | [ResNet101](https://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385) | 93.75% |\n| 5 | [RegNetX_200MF](https://arxiv.org/abs/2003.13678) | 94.24% |\n| 6 | [RegNetY_400MF](https://arxiv.org/abs/2003.13678) | 94.29% |\n| 7 | [MobileNetV2](https://arxiv.org/abs/1801.04381) | 94.43% |\n| 8 | [ResNeXt29(32x4d)](https://arxiv.org/abs/1611.05431) | 94.73% |\n| 9 | [ResNeXt29(2x64d)](https://arxiv.org/abs/1611.05431) | 94.82% |\n| 10 | [SimpleDLA](https://arxiv.org/abs/1707.064) | 94.89% |\n| 11 | [DenseNet121](https://arxiv.org/abs/1608.06993) | 95.04% |\n| 12 | [PreActResNet18](https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.05027) | 95.11% |\n| 13 | [DPN92](https://arxiv.org/abs/1707.01629) | 95.16% |\n| 14 | [DLA](https://arxiv.org/pdf/1707.06484.pdf) | 95.47% |\n\n**Additional notes:**\n\n- The `models/` directory contains **18** Python module files (excluding `__init__.py`). Beyond the 14 above, there are also implementations for **LeNet**, **GoogLeNet**, **ShuffleNet**, **ShuffleNetV2**, **EfficientNet**, **PNASNet**, and **SENet** — but these do **not** have reported accuracies in the README, meaning the author either didn't benchmark them on CIFAR-10 or didn't include the results.\n- All listed accuracy values are for **CIFAR-10** specifically.\n- The top-performing model is **DLA at 95.47%**, while the lightest option with solid accuracy is **MobileNetV2 at 94.43%** — worth considering if inference cost matters for your fine-tuning project.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 862, "prompt_tokens": 5192, "total_tokens": 6054, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 67, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4928, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0008825208, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001325808, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00074994}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863912-a2HQP2LSNg90qYbBAMYV", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3c2-cb21-7fe2-88f8-969e09869352-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5192, "output_tokens": 862, "total_tokens": 6054, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 4928}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 67}}}}]}}}
